data.eml:eml: The genus Setodes Rambur (Trichoptera, Leptoceridae) in Japan

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Katsuma, Nobuyuki (2018): The genus Setodes Rambur (Trichoptera, Leptoceridae) in Japan. Zootaxa 4407 (2): 191-212, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4407.2.2
